Seehofer Says EU Fund Moves Put German Rating at Risk, SZ Says

-- B y   J u l i e   C r u z
-- 
2011-09-28T18:45:37Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-28/seehofer-says-eu-fund-moves-put-german-rating-at-risk-sz-says.html
Germany ’s Christian Social Union
Chairman Horst Seehofer said the expansion of  Europe ’s rescue
fund is putting Germany’s credit rating at risk, Sueddeutsche
Zeitung reported, citing an interview.  Seehofer told the newspaper that “overstretching” the
fund’s powers may put Germany at risk of a credit-rating
downgrade and threatens economic growth.  To contact the reporter on this story:
